      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was walking through the market today and i realized that if i just stopped walking, or if i just... wasn't here tomorrow, the flow of people wouldn't even ripple. like, nobody would even notice a gap. it's weird how much of a non-entity i feel like. just a ghost in a country that doesn't know i exist.",
